        SlotAndLocality poll(ResourceProfile resourceProfile,
                     java.lang.Iterable<TaskManagerLocation> locationPreferences)
        Poll a slot which matches the required resource profile. The polling tries to satisfy the location preferences, by TaskManager and by host.
        参数:
        resourceProfile - The required resource profile.
        locationPreferences - The location preferences, in order to be checked.
        返回:
        Slot which matches the resource profile, null if we can't find a match
